      void CommandLineController.addBike(java.lang.String[] args)
      This method applies command line instructions of the form:
      addBike <networkName> <type> <time>
      or
      addBike <networkName> <stationID> <type> <time> The time has to be on the following format: YYYY-MM-dd HH:mm The type has to be electric or mechanic.

      rentBike <userID> <stationID> <bikeType> <time> <networkName>
      The time has to be on the following format: YYYY-MM-dd HH:mm The type has to be electric or mechanic.

      This method applies command line instructions of the form:

      void CommandLineController.sortStation(java.lang.String[] args)
      This method applies command line instructions of the form:
      sortStation <networkName> <sortingStrategy> <startTime> <endTime>
      startTime and endTime have to be on the following format: YYYY-MM-dd HH:mm The sorting strategy can be more-used or least-occupied.
